After a lifetime of dreaming of traveling the world, 
78-year-old homebody Carl (voiced by Ed Asner) is 
lured into an unbelievable adventure, thanks in part 
to the persistence of Russell, an 8-year-old Wilderness 
Explorer (Jordan Nagai). Together, the unlikely pair 
embarks on a thrilling odyssey full of jungle beasts 
and rough terrain. Other voices include the renowned 
Christopher Plummer and Pixar stalwart John Ratzenberger.

Starring: Edward Asner, Jordan Nagai
